{"tid":2133675,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃之鋒指選舉主任曲解其言論　憂日後指他違港區國安法","createTime":"2020-07-31T08:34:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T08:40:55.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b420615e3e215484c22332dacb00d566758583a3","tid":2133675,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T08:34:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541007-20200731.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541007-20200731.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG130iZiuoirEQNng52NyFBY4%3D&h=eab7b740\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541007-20200731.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=067bc209\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541007-20200731.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒被裁定參選立法會提名無效，他批評，選舉主任為他羅織莫須有罪名，刻意曲解他的言論。<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒說，選舉主任認為他以個人身份，仍繼續推動已解散香港眾志的「民主自決」主張，以過往身份去裁定他有否參選資格，並不合理。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，選舉主任認為反對《港區國安法》就是不擁護《基本法》，並由要求「擁護」變成要「信奉」《基本法》，質疑過往並未有出現過「信奉」的說法，擔心是增加政治紅線。<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒又批評，選舉主任以他在社交平台的「#國際戰線」，及對澳洲取消引渡協議的回應及評論，視為尋求外國干預，是刻意曲解他的言論，憂慮是為日後鋪墊他違反《港區國安法》的藉口。"},{"pid":"9ef5087ec3f599b5a5bff2d16196f389feaab4d4","tid":2133675,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T08:35:08.000Z","msg":"黃之鋒係咪講咗話唔會走？"},{"pid":"2a0025a09347d78781f02c20d01021e98267c64f","tid":2133675,"uid":231908,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9ef5087ec3f599b5a5bff2d16196f389feaab4d4","tid":2133675,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T08:35:08.000Z","msg":"黃之鋒係咪講咗話唔會走？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T08:35:56.000Z","msg":"無，不過佢走唔到，passport係法庭度"},{"pid":"a62481565cc12e2f9a2333579baa5487f3bb4718","tid":2133675,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2a0025a09347d78781f02c20d01021e98267c64f","tid"